3 CONT <b>Literacy programs</b> were introduced on some voyages to "reform" pr
3 CONC isoners — it’s possible Simon had access to basic instruction or religi
3 CONC ous tracts.<b>⚰️ 4. Mortality</b>
3 CONT •
3 CONT Some voyages in the 1830s had <b>no deaths</b>, others had several.
